OL,3,CDecriminalisation of cannabis could be
OL,4,Cdebated next month
OL,6,F's politicians could debate the
OL,7,Fdecriminalisation of for personal and
OL,8,Frecreational use as early as next
OL,9,Fmonth.
OL,11,FA proposition to is calling for the
OL,12,Fdrug to be legal for people aged 18
OL,13,Fand over while limiting the amount
OL,14,Fpeople can possess, where it can be
OL,15,Fused, and how much someone can consume
OL,16,Fwhile driving.
OL,18,FDeputy Tom Coles lodged the 'Cannabis:
OL,19,FDecriminalisation of Personal
OL,20,FPossession and Recreational Use'
OL,21,Fproposition on Friday 24 May 2024.
